<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Projects on Steven Lee · FDE</title><link>https://alitrack.com/projects/</link><description>Recent content in Projects on Steven Lee · FDE</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><atom:link href="https://alitrack.com/projects/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>duckdb_fdw</title><link>https://alitrack.com/projects/duckdb-fdw/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://alitrack.com/projects/duckdb-fdw/</guid><description>&lt;p>让 PostgreSQL 直接查询 DuckDB 数据库的外包装。一条 SQL 跨越 OLTP 和 OLAP。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">CREATE&lt;/span> EXTENSION duckdb_fdw;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">CREATE&lt;/span> SERVER duckdb_server &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">FOREIGN&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">DATA&lt;/span> WRAPPER duckdb_fdw;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">CREATE&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">FOREIGN&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">TABLE&lt;/span> analytics (...) SERVER duckdb_server;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">-- 跨数据库 JOIN
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e">&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">SELECT&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">*&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">FROM&lt;/span> transactions t
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">JOIN&lt;/span> analytics a &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">ON&lt;/span> t.id &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> a.transaction_id;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>被收录入 PostgreSQL 扩展名录，全球 30+ 贡献者。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>MediaForge</title><link>https://alitrack.com/projects/mediaforge/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://alitrack.com/projects/mediaforge/</guid><description>&lt;p>AI 驱动的全自动内容工厂。一篇文章进去，播客、视频、图文卡片出来。&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>5 层架构&lt;/strong>：Ingest → Compose → Synthesize → Render → Publish&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>7 个 TTS 后端&lt;/strong>：Edge TTS, Azure, ElevenLabs, CosyVoice&amp;hellip;&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Agent 驱动&lt;/strong>：LLM 理解内容，自动决定表达方式&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Hyperframes&lt;/strong>：30fps 动画渲染&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>目标：所有内容由 AI agent 生产，人类只负责判断。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>OpenFusion</title><link>https://alitrack.com/projects/openfusion/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://alitrack.com/projects/openfusion/</guid><description>&lt;p>开源多模型融合编排引擎。在自己基础设施上运行，不绑定任何模型供应商。&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Pluggable backends (Anthropic, OpenAI, DeepSeek, Ollama&amp;hellip;)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Cost/latency/rule-based routing&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Response streaming, caching, rate limiting&lt;/li>
&lt;li>OpenAI-compatible API endpoint&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">router&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">:=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">fusion&lt;/span>.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">New&lt;/span>(
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">fusion&lt;/span>.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">WithModel&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;claude-sonnet-4&amp;#34;&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">anthropicBackend&lt;/span>),
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">fusion&lt;/span>.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">WithModel&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;deepseek-v4&amp;#34;&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">deepseekBackend&lt;/span>),
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">fusion&lt;/span>.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">WithStrategy&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">fusion&lt;/span>.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">CostOptimized&lt;/span>),
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>TypePress</title><link>https://alitrack.com/projects/typepress/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://alitrack.com/projects/typepress/</guid><description>&lt;p>纯 Rust 实现的 HTML→PDF 排版引擎。不依赖 Chrome、WebKit 或任何浏览器引擎。&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>HTML parser (html5ever)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Custom CSS cascade + box layout&lt;/li>
&lt;li>PDF backend (printpdf)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>CJK font support with fallback chains&lt;/li>
&lt;li>~15K lines of Rust&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>客户的生产环境没有 GUI——所以不需要浏览器。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>